    },
    "innerText": "3. Saṃbhejjaudakasuttādivaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "76-77"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Sambhijjaṭṭhāne"
      },
      "ti ",
      " sambhijjasamodhānagataṭṭhāne. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Samenti"
      },
      " sametā honti. Tenāha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘samāgacchantī’’"
      },
      "ti. Pāḷiyaṃ vibhattilopena niddesoti tamatthaṃ dassento ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘tīṇi vā’’"
      },
      "ti āha. Sambhijjati missībhāvaṃ gacchati etthāti sambhejjaṃ, missitaṭṭhānaṃ. Tattha udakaṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "sambhejjaudakaṃ"
      },
      ". Tenāha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘sambhinnaṭṭhāne udaka’’"
      },
      "nti."
    ],
    "innerText": "76-77.Sambhijjaṭṭhāneti sambhijjasamodhānagataṭṭhāne. Samenti sametā honti. Tenāha ‘‘samāgacchantī’’ti. Pāḷiyaṃ vibhattilopena niddesoti tamatthaṃ dassento ‘‘tīṇi vā’’ti āha. Sambhijjati missībhāvaṃ gacchati etthāti sambhejjaṃ, missitaṭṭhānaṃ. Tattha udakaṃ sambhejjaudakaṃ. Tenāha ‘‘sambhinnaṭṭhāne udaka’’nti."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Saṃbhejjaudakasuttādivaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
