        "innerText": "Chaṭṭhādīsu vuttanayenevā"
      },
      "ti idha chaṭṭhasuttādīsu paṭhamasuttādīsu vuttanayenevāti attho veditabbo visesābhāvato."
    ],
    "innerText": "Chaṭṭhādīsu vuttanayenevāti idha chaṭṭhasuttādīsu paṭhamasuttādīsu vuttanayenevāti attho veditabbo visesābhāvato."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Pariyosāne"
      },
      "ti imassa abhisamayasaṃyuttassa osānaṭṭhāne. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Aññatitthiyasamaṇabrāhmaṇaparibbājakāna"
      },
      "nti aññatitthiyānaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Guṇādhigamo"
      },
      "ti jhānābhiññāsahito guṇādhigamo. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Satabhāgampi…pe… na upagacchati"
      },
      " saccapaṭivedhassa mahānubhāvattā. Tenāha bhagavā paccakkhasabbadhammo ‘‘evaṃ mahādhigamo, bhikkhave, diṭṭhisampanno puggalo evaṃ mahābhiñño’’ti."
    ],
    "innerText": "Pariyosāneti imassa abhisamayasaṃyuttassa osānaṭṭhāne. Aññatitthiyasamaṇabrāhmaṇaparibbājakānanti aññatitthiyānaṃ. Guṇādhigamoti jhānābhiññāsahito guṇādhigamo. Satabhāgampi…pe… na upagacchati saccapaṭivedhassa mahānubhāvattā. Tenāha bhagavā paccakkhasabbadhammo ‘‘evaṃ mahādhigamo, bhikkhave, diṭṭhisampanno puggalo evaṃ mahābhiñño’’ti."
  },
  {
